'''尼康 D300''' 是一款 12.3 百万像素的专业级 <ref>{{cite web | title =NIKON INTRODUCES THE NEW D300 PROFESSIONAL DIGITAL SLR CAMERA | url =http://press.nikonusa.com/2007/08/nikon_introduces_the_new_d300.php | publisher =Nikon | accessdate =2008-03-23 | deadurl =yes | archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20080309133303/http://press.nikonusa.com/2007/08/nikon_introduces_the_new_d300.php | archivedate =2008-03-09 }}</ref> [[Nikon_DX_格式|Nikon DX 格式]] 数码单镜反光相机 (dSLR) ，与尼康[[Nikon_FX_格式|全画幅]]相机[[尼康D3|D3]]一同发布于2007年8月23日。它在當時被尼康定位于DX格式最顶尖的相机<ref>{{cite web | title =NIKON D300 | url =http://nikonimaging.com/global/products/digitalcamera/slr/d300/index.htm | publisher =Nikon | accessdate =2008-03-23 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20071230015903/http://nikonimaging.com/global/products/digitalcamera/slr/d300/index.htm | archive-date =2007-12-30 | dead-url =yes }}</ref>。它很类似于尼康 D3，最大的区别在于感光元件尺寸的不同，D3为全画幅。但与D3相比D300更实用，兼有高分辨率和高速的优势（连拍速度为6张每秒，而当附加MB-D10电池模块时能够达到8张每秒）。

